Title: Disarmed And Dangerous
Plot: The detectives search for the murderer of FBI agent Billy Ray Jackson, only Billy Ray isn't really an FBI agent, and neither are his impressively capable partners, Miles Baker and Emma Solomon.
GuestStars: David Berman, Liz Vassey, Kurt Caceres, Valentina de Angelis, Jamie Harris, Paula Malcomson, Alex Skuby, Keith Szarabajka, Vince Vieluf, Jon Wellner, Frank Whaley, Matthew Wiese
